data.description: Welcome Home!  As you drive down the private driveway from the cul-de-sac you will enjoy the peace and tranquil setting.   This home has so much to offer!  Enjoy sitting on the front porch or relaxing in the covered back porch.  This home is much larger than it looks.  As you enter the home you will see the huge great room with fireplace and the large dining room.  Also on the main floor is the main bedroom en-suite complete with walk in closet, double vanities. soaking tub and separate shower.  The large open kitchen and breakfast area is also located on the main floor with the laundry room and guest half bath.  Upstairs you will find 2 large bedrooms and bath along with access to the extra space in the walk in Attic.  Downstairs is full of potential with a finished flex room perfect for an office or den, 2 partially finished bedrooms, stubbed and plumbed bathroom. and lots of unfinished space.  Newly renovated with Kitchen LVP flooring and freshly painted inside.  Great Schools are close buy.  Don't let this awesome home get away!
